{"id":"ed1f501f20ac6e0a7f55055fb55889424fc107353493e036f6dd4e9de748601f","item_id":"f63358163f:0","text":"此 pattern 会对输入的矢量置换图案进行分层组合。"}
{"id":"ab2d784205c00c0c8d9164e399c695ce74c478712ac25b69626f46fe59b89c4f","item_id":"f63358163f:1","text":"每个 PxrDispVectorLayer 最多支持 5 个层。若要使用超过 5 个层，可以将一个 PxrDispVectorLayer 节点的结果连接到另一个 PxrDispVectorLayer 节点的输入。"}
{"id":"146afaf26adbf60d21851f4ab67df71e1a69b8893da9e28722a7f9b4b4e2c8a0","item_id":"f63358163f:2","text":"如果需要超过 5 个层，请将一个 PxrDispVectorLayer 节点的结果连接到另一个 PxrDispVectorLayer 节点的输入。"}
{"id":"c763e5bc2fbc45007d421a3d7367c5b91cbb63669de8d22a204a464de7660c19","item_id":"f63358163f:3","text":"需要将结果连接到"}
{"id":"022543dbe3b58a1681fca19925453b701d7a289d04c90ad0f56ea226c7858d89","item_id":"f63358163f:4","text":"PxrDisplace"}
{"id":"0bd6f2411fc77841478d916de96bfdcdbe74718e8c5f5b3335048248dbabd093","item_id":"f63358163f:5","text":" 的 Vector Displacement 输入，才能置换几何体。"}
{"id":"2b65adfeca07880ccff47a555cd44f4571ff234e5721bebfafb441699997eca8","item_id":"f63358163f:7","text":"Overall Gain"}
{"id":"964a440f369f35e8bdb63c8c39e85358f31d2bbc8946fe14226b61c39fe9f53b","item_id":"f63358163f:8","text":"控制最终分层后的矢量置换结果的增益。当需要全局调整所有分层置换值的强度时，这很方便。每个层的增益都会与此参数相乘。"}
{"id":"43224036a8bb3fab67633e101dbb3bae876e63daf0e71ddc5000a6c7434d4511","item_id":"f63358163f:9","text":"Base Layer"}
{"id":"c3b939e5554d5a0c407b7353de5afd02b24912e18a05868c4101757ff4afd614","item_id":"f63358163f:11","text":"默认情况下，基础层处于启用状态。但如果需要调试，可以取消勾选此参数来禁用基础层。取消勾选后，基础层会在分层时被跳过。"}
{"id":"a56708ff58297b3674361420b096629c40fb5b509fd6e553b8642e88bfe7a41f","item_id":"f63358163f:12","text":"Base Layer Gain"}
{"id":"a25e716e2329439ada50fa62479483717b282fd5340ca7a76ecb2f43ec74a7e4","item_id":"f63358163f:13","text":"基础层的 Gain（增益）。"}
{"id":"59c4b604a3370d91d34456efb242e964878898d4abddbc4c7d01aaa2735836d3","item_id":"f63358163f:14","text":"Base Layer Vector"}
{"id":"3da8a76f6fa7953dc1a99f72e0698b152fc3ba1ba073964c4053b15dd4576405","item_id":"f63358163f:15","text":"连接到矢量置换 pattern。它可以是任意 pattern 的矢量或颜色输出结果，例如 resultXYZ 或 resultRGB。"}
{"id":"3f965d3daacbe61a1a5833dd7a5c20f22af296815941519df56def95998544e8","item_id":"f63358163f:16","text":"Layer1"}
{"id":"7269d6a2a55594ef3761b34e2bad0f98f588ce41df66fc3131c4a49b2f64b3d9","item_id":"f63358163f:18","text":"勾选后，启用第 1 层。"}
{"id":"6d5bf6eb9b19904fb5d984583c177f92a5965f3714f6889666f57f090543466e","item_id":"f63358163f:19","text":"Layer 1 Gain"}
{"id":"de1c6605baafcd66d81d0dd0efe35c165cd459b062ce8150681f74e4f7d3f7a5","item_id":"f63358163f:20","text":"第 1 层的 Gain（增益）。"}
{"id":"4a39a7cfd6fe3fe86c591c3a1c27000bfcc99f4b9ffb55d1d948891b2ab8b41e","item_id":"f63358163f:21","text":"Layer 1 Vector"}
{"id":"5bf065aa65de8d4bb84dcb00ba6a75a217e66690c637b3c760a44500b1b0d992","item_id":"f63358163f:22","text":"连接到矢量置换。它可以是任意 pattern 的矢量或颜色输出结果，例如 resultXYZ 或 resultRGB。"}
{"id":"0e00d0bf859028fcac2f3e40461eeecd49100016a9e4938e16f065f096a7a303","item_id":"f63358163f:23","text":"Layer 1 Mask"}
{"id":"4741c16cf13fb3ed3cd58af886da17024417c3630dc22eca39367ced0b5d4f4a","item_id":"f63358163f:24","text":"第 1 层的 Mask。Values（值）越接近零，此层应用得越少。"}
{"id":"88ca3cdc317af507583b670cbfb17051497a1f99ffaeb8d85dd5e3c612c8d343","item_id":"f63358163f:25","text":"Layer 1 Operation"}
{"id":"90d68d37258d522139d6e5f83dd710e72ca88cf9b6512243ad8ad39d312feefe","item_id":"f63358163f:26","text":"选择此层的置换如何与基础层组合。"}
{"id":"23d186984a289fd55b34b3e5da4d73556bba26d8cfc5eb05cb632217c73f64bc","item_id":"f63358163f:27","text":"1: Add - 将第 1 层的每个矢量分量加到基础层。"}
{"id":"f34fafd9d34033c31f617810eb32eddc15313500edcf2eb4b554ad089e1259fd","item_id":"f63358163f:28","text":"2: Over - 将第 1 层的每个矢量分量叠合到基础层之上。"}
{"id":"85849a74c198953803152a0a5fcc10f3adbd89a2976f3eaa6cad0ac0c638369c","item_id":"f63358163f:29","text":"3: Multiply - 将第 1 层的每个矢量分量与基础层相乘。"}
{"id":"016b59415a96c9aff160bc06e7f27a7ccfb91cfe568651cf6941c2cfc5e24a4f","item_id":"f63358163f:30","text":"4: Average - 返回第 1 层与基础层之间每个矢量分量的平均值。"}
{"id":"8bfa3d40e20ee392b6a52b377e07c335f444d76d563932e794bcc84e19f0585c","item_id":"f63358163f:31","text":"5: Min - 返回第 1 层与基础层之间每个矢量分量的最小值。"}
{"id":"0d98864bf7a2926dd0f8e5ff2e1113aa14cb112417f2527b9b899bdefa57ff46","item_id":"f63358163f:32","text":"6: Max - 返回第 1 层与基础层之间每个矢量分量的最大值。"}
{"id":"20c1064f65920b2ced0fe8122c4b313c9ebe646204356b0b4026736648816d70","item_id":"f63358163f:33","text":"Layer2"}
{"id":"9081051775bd795019f5565aec2d2079dca513d4b6db42b99dad366db612f8bf","item_id":"f63358163f:35","text":"勾选后，启用第 2 层。"}
{"id":"9bf705f71c4179ea3b03ea06bb687f7d34fa24bd6e4f6c1965ce462f5cf9cf1b","item_id":"f63358163f:36","text":"Layer 2 Gain"}
{"id":"4f93a839e3348694c576e751696183b449a458ee2edd53ba69d6b396022f047e","item_id":"f63358163f:37","text":"第 2 层的 Gain（增益）。"}
{"id":"b3bc70370aee459de4ffe7a52c17e00f7b071e34e24cb82ad8def248b88d68f5","item_id":"f63358163f:38","text":"Layer 2 Vector"}
{"id":"83404f68b6a9d06177fb8b3dacdb6f375357530eea33934a06eb60bd8e1b0ee6","item_id":"f63358163f:39","text":"连接到矢量置换。它可以是任意输出矢量或颜色结果的 pattern，例如 resultXYZ 或 resultRGB。"}
{"id":"ecf5f93c3404f171ecb07623412640de02de5dae9fcaa2b702a8225341e5c720","item_id":"f63358163f:40","text":"Layer 2 Mask"}
{"id":"aa26d58224a95e6f10c57e5afd18ee422256e0027731f08f7384c46cd35760f6","item_id":"f63358163f:41","text":"第 2 层的 Mask。Values（值）越接近零，此层应用得越少。"}
{"id":"697d2dd971adab2db9a3f77ebe644f82244f86e3450ad1bbab733fefea87cfd8","item_id":"f63358163f:42","text":"Layer 2 Operation"}
{"id":"c486d497a88d2fff8678f04e798ffe6a77b5561c9051f0377843e9f82ab77bfa","item_id":"f63358163f:43","text":"选择此层的置换如何与前一层组合。如果第 1 层未启用，它会与基础层的结果组合。"}
{"id":"776cfa9b3cc9ee849144498ec99e394c598ca2b76fc99882dc3df969f238cd57","item_id":"f63358163f:44","text":"1: Add - 将第 2 层的每个矢量分量加到第 1 层。"}
{"id":"1652ad7ab0d04687ecc0ade55050f0228bad02753a1de4c8bca9a2aa839d0d30","item_id":"f63358163f:45","text":"2: Over - 将第 2 层的每个矢量分量叠合到第 1 层之上。"}
{"id":"f84b22687fec775524f8ac60968ac3b9e29d99be973126780b4ba79508acc41e","item_id":"f63358163f:46","text":"3: Multiply - 将第 2 层的每个矢量分量与第 1 层相乘。"}
{"id":"21f95fbe34b2c75e39963e5d1880e568e04345a117cf79562b1da36ea9fba34f","item_id":"f63358163f:47","text":"4: Average - 返回第 2 层与第 1 层之间每个矢量分量的平均值。"}
{"id":"8aac1724648863992d3988e7bb4a13c54e475c0cd48502a3d20070ecc1635958","item_id":"f63358163f:48","text":"5: Min - 返回第 2 层与第 1 层之间每个矢量分量的最小值。"}
{"id":"6376969a51bad129a443fc331af45ff296428947813e92f4b86d3bc7eafa3dcb","item_id":"f63358163f:49","text":"6: Max - 返回第 2 层与第 1 层之间每个矢量分量的最大值。"}
{"id":"ecb5ee1941ffc6785f588507c60c0debc247005fd717ecef945789a359049454","item_id":"f63358163f:50","text":"Layer 3 to 4"}
{"id":"e05ef3cd358ba27c85c6b6e70c207e5ffa72b50792a141f5205fdfe43e16b2cb","item_id":"f63358163f:51","text":"参数与 Layer 2 类似。"}
{"id":"f3c2e0cb416a2cc1652481a52b5d55975473472d6839077e80829736ac8cbefb","item_id":"f63358163f:54","text":"矢量结果。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "f63358163f:6", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "92c1cdfdf4cb9cf6fcca962f206de36fd5d60db1178bc9461052f8de703a0e06", "item_id": "f63358163f:10", "text": "Enabled"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "f63358163f:52", "text": "Output Parameters"}
{"id": "35f6e1ebb9b040db4e992f8d8fb554d4bc9ad8ea924c6744adc8ae3f58bc3498", "item_id": "f63358163f:53", "text": "resultXYZ"}
{"id": "db7dd1ce0d7ea86988255ca35194b0f1bd3ac901a577cbf001917e21a93cd36c", "item_id": "f63358163f:55", "text": "resultX"}
{"id": "29ae71f9ed673ba0ac9f0665be3a580e22f3730cc133352d450ae293b0912204", "item_id": "f63358163f:56", "text": "来自 resultXYZ 输出的 X 分量。"}
{"id": "1559ea0c7d8aa4ad51badbe1b30a3a5d7b82932753dbc63044d02897c487480c", "item_id": "f63358163f:57", "text": "resultY"}
{"id": "d123f179f225b75f5c31d8eb27e55d3e111c3dcb113e1b574dcb3c6f0d2e9162", "item_id": "f63358163f:58", "text": "来自 resultXYZ 输出的 Y 分量。"}
{"id": "153df47561d2ede586a69b0186936cf344555bcbef47ecadd8fbf8b7ce5b2672", "item_id": "f63358163f:59", "text": "resultZ"}
{"id": "862a07bec45906d80eb88bd5c5e3e88c294baf8437e127dce1ee92ec7d457d62", "item_id": "f63358163f:60", "text": "来自 resultXYZ 输出的 Z 分量。"}
